Use of ChatGPT in Education (Research)
text:
Hi, I'm an undergraduate student, and in a few weeks have the opportunity to conduct some research on the use and effects of ChatGPT on a large sample of students.

I wanted to ask if anyone has some unanswered questions regarding the use of ChatGPT, affecting student performance and confidence in exams. These could be related to any topic, things we could gather data on, or just your thoughts :)

I precisely leave out some key details in this post, just so i recieve the most unbiased, unfiltered, just raw thoughts from the community.

Special thanks!!!
